  "title": "Administrative Admin |School |West Coast Road",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>1. Front desk reception duties such as answering/ transferring phone calls</p><p>and attending to walk-in parents/students/vendors.</p><p>2. Issuing of keys to staff if require the use of special rooms.</p><p>3. Record details of students and attend to students who are unwell at</p><p>sickbay.</p><p>4. Contact parents to update student who is unwell.</p><p>5. Record details of students who leave school early due to sickness and/or</p><p>have medical appointment and ensure that Early Dismissal form is</p><p>completed.</p><p>6. Record details of lost & found Items in the Lost & Found form and track</p><p>movements at the end of every school term.</p><p>7. Receive delivery items and inform staff on collection from General Office.</p><p>8. Collate list of students who have not collected their testimonials.</p><p>9. Manage the movement of school uniform on loan to students.</p><p>10.Distribute the mailers and any other materials required.</p><p>11.Prepare and count food coupons for payment if required.</p><p>12.Perform any ad-hoc administrative duties when required.</p>",
